Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:22.90,Title,,0,0,0,,{\1cB699FF\4c85A99A\shad4\3aFF\fn方正屏显雅宋_GBK\b1\fs115\fsp30\blur3\pos(1340,1078)}自行车
